<div class="Plug_and_Play">
  <h2>Plug-and-Play</h2>
  <p class="Plug_and_Play_text">To access a more comprehensive installation tutorial, please visit</p>
  <a href="https://deepernetwork.in/pages/install-deeper-network" class="deeper_buy_now" target="_blank"
    >install.deepernetwork ></a
  >
  <div class="Plug_and_Play_list">
    <div class="Plug_and_Play_item">
      <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_img">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="https://cdn.shopifycdn.net/s/files/1/0256/1038/7504/files/picoV5-01.gif?v=1702864562"
          alt="Virtual Wire Mode"
        >
      </div>
      <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_content">
        <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_title">Virtual Wire Mode</div>

        <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_text">
          Suitable for homes with both a modem and router. Install Deeper Connect directly between them, maintaining
          your existing Wi-Fi while enabling DPN services.
        </div>
        <a href="" class="mode_link"> learn more </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="Plug_and_Play_item">
      <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_img">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="https://cdn.shopifycdn.net/s/files/1/0256/1038/7504/files/picoV5-02_077be236-ec6d-47e9-aa15-63c8842e1574.gif?v=1702864561"
          alt="Virtual Wire Mode"
        >
      </div>
      <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_content">
        <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_title">Router Mode</div>

        <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_text">
          Ideal for homes with integrated modem/routers.Deeper Connect serves as a second router for DpNservices,
          requiring connection to DeeperWiFi.
        </div>
        <a href="" class="mode_link"> learn more </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="Plug_and_Play_item">
      <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_img">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="https://cdn.shopifycdn.net/s/files/1/0256/1038/7504/files/picoV5-03_0c7f9105-ef39-4ae3-8ede-5ef20aaf265d.gif?v=1702864560"
          alt="Virtual Wire Mode"
        >
      </div>
      <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_content">
        <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_title">Wifi Adapter Mode</div>

        <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_text">
          Great for home Wi-Fi or public hotspots, such as hotels, cafes, and airports. Deeper Connect acts as a USB
          Wi-Fi adapter, letting you connect to home Wi-Fi or the public Wi-Fi without DeeperWiFi.
        </div>
        <a href="" class="mode_link"> learn more </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="Plug_and_Play_item">
      <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_img">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0256/1038/7504/files/picoV5-03_-1225-2.gif?v=1721025541"
          alt="Virtual Wire Mode"
        >
      </div>
      <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_content">
        <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_title">Wireless Relay Mode</div>

        <div class="Plug_and_Play_item_text">
          Perfect for home Wi-Fi or public hotspots like hotels, cafes, and airports. Deeper Connect connects to home
          Wi-Fi or the public Wi-Fi, and users need to connect to DeeperWiFi to use DPN services.
        </div>
        <a href="" class="mode_link"> learn more </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

